    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is very sound; the engine runs smoothly, the brakes are responsive, and the transmission shifts without any hesitation. The interior is clean with only minor signs of use, and while the exterior has a few small stone chips and light surface scratches, it still presents very well. It is a reliable choice for anyone looking for a car that is ready to hit the road immediately with no major repairs needed.",
